profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.

profile:
“Finally, a Home Inspection Service that Gives Me a TRUE, Quality Home Assessment”

• Get explicit insight from 4 certified Tradesmen! Our Knowledge & Experience Can’t be Beat!

• The Trade Inspectors remove the possibility of any issues getting overlooked, which often happens in a standard visual home inspection.

• Trade Inspectors can assess deficiencies, and help you understand why the problem is occurring.

• Find out if your home is Eco friendly and energy efficient

“But what can the Trade Inspectors do than a Regular home inspector cannot?”

• Trade Inspectors do full well and septic inspections. We camera septic beds and ALL main drains to divulge any blockage, tree roots, or other possible deficiencies.

• Trade Inspectors can legally inspect the heat exchanger with an inspection camera. This will reveal the safety and efficiency of the furnace and any risk of carbon monoxide.

• Trade Inspectors can remove electrical panels and properly assess the source of any deficiencies

• Trade Inspectors use an infrared camera to detect any moisture, or water leakage behind drywall as well as detect any cracks in the foundation of the home.

This is just 4, of many tasks, Trade Inspectors are qualified to perform.

Check us out online to see a full 250 point inspection checklist that we perform on every house.

When it Comes to Your Home, Don’t Deal With A Jack of All Trades… Deal WITH the Trades!!

Call Today To Book Your Inspection
705-243-6699
